<div class="span12">
  <div id="description" class="row">
    <div class="span12">
      <h2>Smart meter web application evaluation.</h2>
      <h4>Hello and thank you for taking the time to help me with my honours project!</h4>
      <h4>Background</h4>
      <p>
        As part of my honours project I have developed a software which provides the same functionality as the meters that will be going into homes and it will be used as part of a major project - <a href="http://www.energyoracle.org/">IDEAL project</a> at the <a href="http://www.ed.ac.uk/">University of Edinburgh</a>. This project will focus on examining the effect of providing personalised behavioural feedback to occupants: explicitly identifying the behaviours (e.g., showering and bathing, room heating, major appliance use) that account for energy use/expenditure; and how these could be reduced.
      </p>
      <h4>My project</h4>
      <p>
        As mentioned above, this web application is supposed to mimic the functionality provided by the smart meters that will be installed as part of the Smart Meter programme. That functionality includes displaying information about the energy(gas and electricity) usage such as: 
        <ul>
          <li>energy usage</li>
          <li>energy cost</li>
          <li>carbon footprint</li>
        </ul>
      </p>
      <h4>The Evaluation</h4>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div id="survey" class="row">
    <div class="span12">
      <!-- <h2>Smart meter web application evaluation.</h2> -->
        <iframe src="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1ddQznpYcJEBs6fxJ4I1rfeB9QOUCz5zOWuDXj8LpAVA/viewform?embedded=true" width="920" height="580" frameborder="0" marginheight="0" marginwidth="0">Loading...</iframe>

    <input class="btn" id="proceed_eval" type="button" value="Show the app"> 
    </div>
  </div>
  <div id="graph" style="display: none;">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="span10">
        <div class="row">
          <div id="chart_container" class="span10" style="height: 500px;">
          </div>
        </div>
        <div id="chart_controls" class="row">
          <div class="period-shown">
            <%= hidden_field_tag "type", @type %>
            <%= hidden_field_tag "date", @date %>
            <%= hidden_field_tag "unit", @unit %>
          </div>
      <!--    <div class="span4">
             <%= select  "chart", 
                        "type", 
                        CHART_TYPES, 
                        selected: current_user.try(:chart_type) || "column" %>
          </div> -->
          <div class="span3">
            <input class="graph_nav pull-left btn-primary btn span2" disabled="true" id="prev_period" type="button" value="Previous"> 
          </div>
          <div class="span4">
            <span class="pull-left">
              Toggle: 
            </span>
            <%= check_box_tag "carbon_intensity_toggler", "carbon_intensity", false, class: "pull-left chart-toggler", color: 5, axis_n: 2, series_type: "line" %>
            <%= label_tag "carbon_intensity_toggler", "CO2 intensity", class: "pull-left" %>
            
            <%= check_box_tag "carbon_toggler", "carbon_result", false, class: "pull-left chart-toggler", color: 6, axis_n: 1, series_type: "spline" %>
            <%= label_tag "carbon_toggler", "CO2 emissions", class: "pull-left" %>
          </div>
          <div class="span2" style="display: none;" >
            <%= check_box_tag "usage_toggler", "amount", false, class: "pull-left chart-toggler", color: 6, axis_n: 1, series_type: "spline" %>
            <%= label_tag "usage_toggler", "Energy usage", class: "pull-left" %>      
          </div>
          <div class="span2" style="display: none;" >
            <%= check_box_tag "price_toggler", "price", false, class: "pull-left chart-toggler", color: 5, axis_n: 2, series_type: "line" %>
            <%= label_tag "price_toggler", "Energy price", class: "pull-left" %>
          </div>
          <div class="span3">
            <input class="graph_nav pull-right btn-primary btn span2" disabled="true" id="next_period" type="button" value="Next"> 
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="span2">
        <input class="span2 btn-success btn" id="reset_graph" type="button" value="Reset graph"> 
        <div class="span2 right_container">
          Totals for the period:
          <span id="date" class="totals">All time</span> <br/>
          Cost: <br/> 
          <span id="energy_cost" class="totals">###</span> <br/>
          Usage: <br/> 
          <span id="amount" class="totals">###</span> <br/>
          CO2 generated: <br/> 
          <span id="carbon_result" class="totals">###</span> <br/>        
        </div>

        <div id="comparison_container" style="display: none;" class="span2 right_container">
          Compare to: <br/>
          <label id="last_period" class="checkbox">
            <%= check_box_tag "last_period", "", false, class: "comparison_toggler" %>
            <span>Previous year</span>
          </label>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  
  </div>
</div>
